data.title: Transformers: Age of Extinction
data.text: A mechanic and his family join the Autobots as they are targeted by a bounty hunter from another world.

data.title: Game of Thrones
data.text: Seven noble families fight for control of the mythical land of Westeros.

data.title: Orange Is the New Black
data.text: The story of Piper Chapman, a woman in her thirties who is sentenced to fifteen months in prison after being convicted of a decade-old crime of transporting money for her drug-dealing girlfriend.

data.title: The Fault in Our Stars
data.text: Hazel and Gus are two teenagers who share an acerbic wit, a disdain for the conventional, and a love that sweeps them on a journey. Their relationship is all the more miraculous given that Hazel's other constant companion is an oxygen tank, Gus jokes about his prosthetic leg, and they met and fell in love at a cancer support group.

data.title: How to Train Your Dragon 2
data.text: When Hiccup and Toothless discover an ice cave that is home to hundreds of new wild dragons and the mysterious Dragon Rider, the two friends find themselves at the center of a battle to protect the peace.

data.title: The Leftovers
data.text: Revolves around mysterious disappearances, world-wide, and specifically follows a group of people who are left behind in the suburban community of Mapleton. They must begin to rebuild their lives after the loss of more than 100 people.

data.title: Dawn of the Planet of the Apes
data.text: A growing nation of genetically evolved apes led by Caesar is threatened by a band of human survivors...

data.title: Tammy
data.text: After losing her job and learning that her husband has been unfaithful, a woman hits the road with her profane, hard-drinking grandmother.

data.title: 22 Jump Street
data.text: After making their way through high school (twice), big changes are in store for officers Schmidt and Jenko when they go deep undercover at a local college.

data.title: Foxcatcher
data.text: Based on the true story of Mark Schultz, an Olympic wrestler whose relationship with sponsor John du Pont and brother Dave Schultz would lead to unlikely circumstances.

data.title: The Hunger Games: Mockingjay - Part 1
data.text: Katniss Everdeen reluctantly becomes the symbol of a mass rebellion against the autocratic Capitol.

data.title: Dracula Untold
data.text: The origin story of the man who becomes Dracula.

data.title: Maleficent
data.text: A vengeful fairy is driven to curse an infant princess, only to discover that the child may be the one person who can restore peace to their troubled land.

data.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
data.text: Four mutant warriors fight to save their city from an evil kingpin.

data.title: Deliver Us from Evil
data.text: NY police officer Ralph Sarchie investigates a series of crimes. He joins forces with an unconventional priest, schooled in the rituals of exorcism, to combat the possessions that are terrorizing their city.

data.title: X-Men: Days of Future Past
data.text: The X-Men send Wolverine to the past in a desperate effort to change history and prevent an event that results in doom for both humans and mutants.

data.title: True Blood
data.text: Telepathic waitress Sookie Stackhouse encounters a strange new supernatural world when she meets the mysterious Bill, a southern Louisiana gentleman and vampire.

data.title: Edge of Tomorrow
data.text: An officer finds himself caught in a time loop in a war with an alien race. His skills increase as he faces the same brutal combat scenarios, and his union with a Special Forces warrior gets him closer and closer to defeating the enemy.

data.title: Penny Dreadful
data.text: Explorer Sir Malcolm Murray, American gunslinger Ethan Chandler, and others unite to combat supernatural threats in Victorian London.

data.title: Breaking Bad
data.text: To provide for his family's future after he is diagnosed with lung cancer, a chemistry genius turned high school teacher teams up with an ex-student to cook and sell the world's purest crystal meth.

data.title: Life After Beth
data.text: Zach is devastated after his girlfriend, Beth, unexpectedly dies. When she suddenly rises from the dead, he sees it as a second chance and decides to do and say every thing he wishes he had while she was still alive.

data.title: The Lego Movie
data.text: An ordinary Lego construction worker, thought to be the prophesied 'Special', is recruited to join a quest to stop an evil tyrant from gluing the Lego universe into eternal stasis.

data.title: The Walking Dead
data.text: Police officer Rick Grimes leads a group of survivors in a world overrun by zombies.

data.title: Guardians of the Galaxy
data.text: In the far reaches of space, an American pilot named Peter Quill finds himself the object of a manhunt after stealing an orb coveted by the villainous Ronan.

data.title: Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice
data.text: The plot has not been disclosed at this time.

data.title: Divergent
data.text: In a world divided by factions based on virtues, Tris learns she's Divergent and won't fit in. When she discovers a plot to destroy Divergents, Tris and the mysterious Four must find out what makes Divergents dangerous before it's too late.

data.title: Under the Skin
data.text: A mysterious woman seduces lonely men in the evening hours in Scotland. Events lead her to begin a process of self-discovery.

data.title: Dominion
data.text: Follows the perilous journey of a rebellious young soldier who discovers he's the unlikely savior of humanity.

data.title: Doctor Who
data.text: The further adventures of the time traveling alien adventurer and his companions.

data.title: The Expendables 3
data.text: Barney and his team, known as "The Expendables", come into conflict with ruthless arms dealer Conrad Stonebanks, the Expendables' co-founder, who is determined to destroy the team.

data.title: Fury
data.text: April, 1945. As the Allies make their final push in the European Theatre, a battle-hardened army sergeant named Wardaddy commands a Sherman tank and her five-man crew on a deadly mission behind enemy lines. Outnumbered and out-gunned, and with a rookie soldier thrust into their platoon, Wardaddy and his men face overwhelming odds in their heroic attempts to strike at the heart of Nazi Germany.

data.title: Under the Dome
data.text: An invisible and mysterious force field descends upon a small fictional town in the United States, trapping residents inside, cut off from the rest of civilization. The trapped townsfolk must discover the secrets and purpose of the "dome" and its origins, while coming to learn more than they ever knew about each other.

data.title: Pretty Little Liars
data.text: Four friends band together against an anonymous foe who threatens to reveal their darkest secrets, while unraveling the mystery of the murder of their best friend.

data.title: Avengers: Age of Ultron
data.text: The Avengers reassemble to battle the sentient robot known as Ultron.

data.title: Jersey Boys
data.text: The story of four young men from the wrong side of the tracks in New Jersey who came together to form the iconic 1960s rock group The Four Seasons.

data.title: Teen Wolf
data.text: A somewhat awkward teen is attacked by a werewolf and inherits the curse itself, as well as the enemies that come with it.

data.title: The Grand Budapest Hotel
data.text: The adventures of Gustave H, a legendary concierge at a famous European hotel between the wars, and Zero Moustafa, the lobby boy who becomes his most trusted friend.

data.title: Suits
data.text: On the run from a drug deal gone bad, Mike Ross, a brilliant college-dropout, finds himself a job working with Harvey Specter, one of New York City's best lawyers.

data.title: Sex Tape
data.text: A married couple wake up to discover that the sex tape they made the evening before has gone missing, leading to a frantic search for its whereabouts.

data.title: Road to Paloma
data.text: Wolf, a Native American on the run after avenging his mother's murder, flees across the desolate American West on his motorcycle, where he'll discover that justice has a cost.

data.title: Girl Meets World
data.text: A decade after "Boy Meets World," Cory and Topanga Matthews are married and have two children. Their daughter, Riley, faces life lessons through her family, friends, and school, as her parents did when they were younger.

data.title: Earth to Echo
data.text: After receiving a bizarre series of encrypted messages, a group of kids embark on an adventure with an alien who needs their help.

data.title: Once Upon a Time
data.text: A woman with a troubled past is drawn to a New England town where fairy tales are to be believed.

data.title: Arrow
data.text: Spoiled billionaire playboy Oliver Queen is missing and presumed dead when his yacht is lost at sea. He returns five years later a changed man, determined to clean up the city as a hooded vigilante armed with a bow.

data.title: The Big Bang Theory
data.text: A woman who moves into an apartment across the hall from two brilliant but socially awkward physicists shows them how little they know about life outside of the laboratory.

data.title: Transformers
data.text: An ancient struggle between two Cybertronian races, the heroic Autobots and the evil Decepticons, comes to Earth, with a clue to the ultimate power held by a teenager.

data.title: The Prince
data.text: A retired assassin is drawn back into the life he gave up when his daughter is kidnapped. To rescue her, he must confront his former rival.

data.title: Frozen
data.text: Fearless optimist Anna teams up with Kristoff in an epic journey, encountering Everest-like conditions, and a hilarious snowman named Olaf in a race to find Anna's sister Elsa, whose icy powers have trapped the kingdom in eternal winter.

data.title: Supernatural
data.text: Two brothers follow their father's footsteps as "hunters" fighting evil supernatural beings of many kinds including monsters, demons, and gods that roam the earth.

data.title: Neighbors
data.text: A couple with a newborn baby face unexpected difficulties after they are forced to live next to a fraternity house.

data.title: Think Like a Man Too
data.text: All the couples are back for a wedding in Las Vegas, but plans for a romantic weekend go awry when their various misadventures get them into some compromising situations that threaten to derail the big event.

data.title: Horrible Bosses 2
data.text: Dale, Kurt and Nick decide to start their own business but things don't go as planned because of a slick investor, prompting the trio to pull off a harebrained and misguided kidnapping scheme.

data.title: Tyrant
data.text: Series tells the story of an unassuming American family drawn into the workings of a turbulent Middle Eastern nation.

data.title: Into the Storm
data.text: A group of high school students document the events and aftermath of a devastating tornado.

data.title: The Last Ship
data.text: The crew of a naval destroyer is forced to confront the reality of a new existence when a pandemic kills off most of the earth's population.

data.title: Snowpiercer
data.text: In a future where a failed global-warming experiment kills off all life on the planet except for a lucky few that boarded the Snowpiercer, a train that travels around the globe, where a class system evolves.

data.title: The Disappearance of Eleanor Rigby: Them
data.text: One couple's story as they try to reclaim the life and love they once knew and pick up the pieces of a past that may be too far gone.

data.title: Fargo
data.text: A drifter named Lorne Malvo arrives in small-town Minnesota and influences the population with his malice and violence, including put-upon insurance salesman Lester Nygaard.

data.title: 300: Rise of an Empire
data.text: Greek general Themistokles leads the charge against invading Persian forces led by mortal-turned-god Xerxes and Artemisia, vengeful commander of the Persian navy.

data.title: Captain America: The Winter Soldier
data.text: Steve Rogers struggles to embrace his role in the modern world and battles a new threat from old history: the Soviet agent known as the Winter Soldier.

data.title: Lone Survivor
data.text: Marcus Luttrell and his team set out on a mission to capture or kill notorious Taliban leader Ahmad Shah, in late June 2005. Marcus and his team are left to fight for their lives in one of the most valiant efforts of modern warfare.

data.title: Transcendence
data.text: A scientist's drive for artificial intelligence, takes on dangerous implications when his consciousness is uploaded into one such program.

data.title: The Killing
data.text: A police investigation, the saga of a grieving family, and a Seattle mayoral campaign all interlock after the body of 17-year-old Rosie Larsen is found in the trunk of a submerged car.

data.title: Transformers: Dark of the Moon
data.text: The Autobots learn of a Cybertronian spacecraft hidden on the moon, and race against the Decepticons to reach it and to learn its secrets.

data.title: Chef
data.text: A chef who loses his restaurant job starts up a food truck in an effort to reclaim his creative promise, while piecing back together his estranged family.

data.title: Sherlock
data.text: A modern update finds the famous sleuth and his doctor partner solving crime in 21st century London.

data.title: 24: Live Another Day
data.text: Jack Bauer comes out of hiding in London to head off a massive terrorist attack while being hunted down by American forces dispatched by President James Heller.

data.title: Witches of East End
data.text: Centers on the adventures of a mother and her two adult daughters, both of whom unknowingly are their family's next generation of witches...

data.title: The Skeleton Twins
data.text: After ten years of estrangement, twins Maggie and Milo coincidentally cheat death on the same day, prompting...

data.title: Lucy
data.text: A woman, accidentally caught in a dark deal, turns the tables on her captors and transforms into a merciless warrior evolved beyond human logic.

data.title: True Detective
data.text: The lives of two detectives, Rust Cohle and Martin Hart, become entangled during a 17-year hunt for a serial killer in Louisiana.

data.title: A Million Ways to Die in the West
data.text: As a cowardly farmer begins to fall for the mysterious new woman in town, he must put his new-found courage to the test when her husband, a notorious gun-slinger, announces his arrival.

data.title: House of Cards
data.text: A Congressman works with his equally conniving wife to exact revenge on the people who betrayed him.

data.title: Falling Skies
data.text: Survivors of an alien attack on earth gather together to fight for their lives and fight back.

data.title: The Wolf of Wall Street
data.text: Based on the true story of Jordan Belfort, from his rise to a wealthy stock-broker living the high life to his fall involving crime, corruption and the federal government.

data.title: The Flash
data.text: A TV show centered around scientist Barry Allen, who suffers a freak accident that turns him into a superhero with the power of incredible speed.

data.title: American Horror Story
data.text: An anthology series that centers on different characters and locations, including a haunted house, an insane asylum, a witch coven and a freak show.

data.title: Godzilla
data.text: The world's most famous monster is pitted against malevolent creatures who, bolstered by humanity's scientific arrogance, threaten our very existence.

data.title: They Came Together
data.text: When Joel and Molly meet, it's hate at first sight: his big Corporate Candy Company threatens to shut down her quirky indie shop...

data.title: Rio 2
data.text: It's a jungle out there for Blu, Jewel and their three kids after they're hurtled from Rio de Janeiro to the wilds of the Amazon. As Blu tries to fit in, he goes beak-to-beak with the vengeful Nigel, and meets his father-in-law.

data.title: The Raid 2: Berandal
data.text: Only a short time after the first raid, Rama goes undercover with the thugs of Jakarta and plans to bring down the syndicate and uncover the corruption within his police force.

data.title: The Counselor
data.text: A lawyer finds himself in over his head when he gets involved in drug trafficking.

data.title: The Vampire Diaries
data.text: A high school girl is torn between two vampire brothers.

data.title: Hercules
data.text: Having endured his legendary twelve labors, Hercules, the Greek demigod, has his life as a sword-for-hire tested when the King of Thrace and his daughter seek his aid in defeating a tyrannical warlord.

data.title: Grey's Anatomy
data.text: A drama centered on the personal and professional lives of five surgical interns and their supervisors.

data.title: Californication
data.text: A self-loathing, alcoholic writer attempts to repair his damaged relationships with his daughter and her mother while combating sex addiction, a budding drug problem, and the seeming inability to avoid making bad decisions.

data.title: Her
data.text: A lonely writer develops an unlikely relationship with his newly purchased operating system that's designed to meet his every need.

data.title: Sons of Anarchy
data.text: A man in his early 30s struggles to find a balance in his life between being a new dad and his involvement in a motorcycle club.

data.title: Independence Day
data.text: The aliens are coming and their goal is to invade and destroy. Fighting superior technology, Man's best weapon is the will to survive.

data.title: Begin Again
data.text: A chance encounter between a disgraced music-business executive and a young singer-songwriter new to Manhattan turns into a promising collaboration between the two talents.

data.title: Dexter
data.text: A Miami police forensics expert moonlights as a serial killer of criminals whom he believes have escaped justice.

data.title: Defiance
data.text: In the year 2046, it's a new Earth - with new rules. Over thirty years after various alien races arrived on Earth...

data.title: How I Met Your Mother
data.text: Ted searches for the woman of his dreams in New York City with the help of his four best friends.

data.title: Non-Stop
data.text: An air marshal springs into action during a transatlantic flight after receiving a series of text messages that put his fellow passengers at risk unless the airline transfers $150 million into an off-shore account.

data.title: Enemy
data.text: A man seeks out his exact look-alike after spotting him in a movie.

data.title: The 100
data.text: Set 97 years after a nuclear war has destroyed civilization, when a spaceship housing humanity's lone survivors sends 100 juvenile delinquents back to Earth in hopes of possibly re-populating the planet.

data.title: Frank
data.text: Jon, a young wanna-be musician, discovers he's bitten off more than he can chew when he joins an eccentric pop band led by the mysterious and enigmatic Frank.

data.title: Before I Go to Sleep
data.text: A woman wakes up every day, remembering nothing as a result of a traumatic accident in her past. One day, new terrifying truths emerge that force her to question everyone around her.

data.title: Blended
data.text: After a bad blind date, a man and woman find themselves stuck together at a resort for families, where their attraction grows as their respective kids benefit from the burgeoning relationship.

data.title: We're the Millers
data.text: A veteran pot dealer creates a fake family as part of his plan to move a huge shipment of weed into the U.S. from Mexico.
